  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Cut the phyllo dough into small squares and bake until golden brown.",
    "In a large skillet, stir-fry the cherry tomatoes and basil in olive oil until tender.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the baked phyllo dough, stir-fried tomatoes, and sliced mozzarella cheese.",
    "Drizzle the honey over the top of the panzanella and sprinkle with malted milk powder.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional basil if desired.",
    "Store any leftovers in an airtight container in the refrigerator."
